# Bringup probe sequence: count successful initialisations.
*bringup(probes as Vec of i64, n as i64) returns i64
    ok is 0
    i is 0
    while i < n
        if probes.get(i) equals 1
            ok is ok + 1
        i is i + 1
    ok

*main
    p is vec()
    p.push(1)
    p.push(1)
    p.push(0)
    p.push(1)
    p.push(1)
    p.push(0)
    log bringup(p, 6)
